<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>China News | Today's Breaking Stories | Reuters</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/reuters/world/china" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description>Reuters.com is your online source for the latest China news stories and current events, ensuring our readers up to date with any breaking news developments - Powered by RSSHub</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>contact@rsshub.app (RSSHub)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://www.reuters.com/pf/resources/images/reuters/logo-vertical-default-512x512.png?d=116</url><title>China News | Today's Breaking Stories | Reuters</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:29:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>180</ttl><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">6WX4JNPBENK6FLJYPQEO74WLAE</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:43 GMT</pubDate><author>Michael Church</author><category>Sports</category><category>Soccer</category></item><item><title>香港法院驳回媒体大亨黎智英推翻定罪的请求</title><description>香港最高法院周一一致驳回了推翻媒体大亨黎智英和其他六名民主运动人士2019年未经授权集会定罪的请求。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-by-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-overturn-conviction-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">2ODO6I3LYBPU3GLCHKS2FXQD5A</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:16 GMT</pubDate><author>Jessie Pang</author><category>World</category><category>China</category></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国佳兆业集团清算听证会</title><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 9 月 9 日，这使得这家陷入困境的中国开发商有更多时间与一些债券持有人就其债务重组计划达成协议。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">QPLK2J2Y5FIMDGI4EG6LGOHLUU</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 01:49:26 GMT</pubDate><author>Clare Jim, Yu Xie</author><category>Sustainability</category><category>Boards, Policy &amp; Regulation</category></item><item><title>美国通胀数据公布前亚洲股市上涨</title><description>亚洲股市周一小幅走高，原因是日本的假期消除了近期波动的一个根源，投资者等待美国和中国的主要经济数据，以了解全球增长前景的最新情况。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">FKOCLMBSKZOJ5L5HEWFMJJJHDU</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:24:39 GMT</pubDate><author>Wayne Cole</author><category>Markets</category></item><item><title>央行与债券多头对峙，中国债券市场动荡</title><description>中国央行一再警告称，随着投资者追逐政府债券、逃离动荡的股票和不断下滑的房地产市场，可能存在破坏稳定的泡沫风险。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">GF4RXOA3LFIBVLVZVAX7ADDDOM</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:04:55 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Sustainability</category><category>Boards, Policy &amp; Regulation</category></item><item><title>壳牌与中石油将扩建澳大利亚苏拉特煤层气项目</title><description>英国石油和天然气巨头壳牌和中石油周一表示，在呼吁增加投资以增加当地能源供应的背景下，壳牌和中石油已决定扩大昆士兰州苏拉特煤层气项目（SGP）。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/shell-invest-phase-2-surat-gas-project-australia-2024-08-12/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">DANBNMWFFBPDLBQRDO2AMJFDQA</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:00:31 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Business</category><category>Energy</category></item><item><title>外交部长表示，中国支持伊朗捍卫安全</title><description>据中国外交部的一份声明称，中国外交部长王毅周日在电话中告诉伊朗代理外长，中国支持伊朗捍卫其“主权、安全和民族尊严”。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">V6777RGMHVNAPPSDKQT43DCLIA</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:21:36 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>World</category></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国空军的行动“非法”、“鲁莽”</title><description>中国表示，菲律宾扰乱了其训练，并指责马尼拉“非法侵入”其领空。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">MKDPESN4KRM4LLJT63TZKZZBSA</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:39:41 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>菲律宾与中国就南海问题进行贸易指责</title><description>这是自2022年小费迪南德·马科斯总统就任以来菲律宾首次抱怨中国飞机的危险行为。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">VQILWDOQAVI7JCVBGTH4TBMOWE</guid><pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 09:26:58 GMT</pubDate><author>Neil Morales</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>中国火箭解体使1000多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险</title><description>分析人士周五表示，中国的一枚火箭级本周在太空中解体，产生了 700 多块碎片，使地球轨道交通繁忙区域的 1000 多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险碰撞的风险。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">VSYNV3BSUVPB7P4NEKMSTRQDXQ</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:03:13 GMT</pubDate><author>Joey Roulette</author><category>Space</category></item><item><title>央行称将增加国债交易</title><description>中国人民银行还将寻求降低企业融资和家庭信贷成本。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-says-it-will-increase-treasury-bond-trading-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">UZWROSOA2ZNIZJFQIZDC3N6UEE</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 18:47:11 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Markets</category><category>Rates &amp; Bonds</category></item><item><title>欧盟高管表示调查仍在继续，相信其中国电动汽车措施符合世贸组织</title><description>欧盟执行机构周五表示，欧盟委员会相信其对中国电动汽车国家补贴的调查和针对中国电动汽车补贴的措施符合世界贸易组织的规则，并将继续进行调查。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-executive-confident-its-chinese-ev-measures-comply-with-wto-says-probe-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">3GPSO6ZKJRIDXDGB4P5YDOVWRQ</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 15:37:08 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Business</category><category>Autos &amp; Transportation</category></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人要求投资者加入重组程序</title><description>中国恒大在周五提交的文件中表示，其清算人已邀请有兴趣重组这家负债累累的房地产开发商或其任何部分的投资者。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrandes-liquidators-ask-investors-join-restructuring-process-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">CQM25NG5CJOHNG5RL63NVSVOZA</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:48:54 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Business</category><category>Finance</category></item><item><title>菲律宾与越南举行首次海岸警卫队联合演习</title><description>周五，菲律宾和越南船只的船员用水炮轰击一艘船只，并模拟搜救，这是两国海岸警卫队在南海与北京对峙的首次联合演习。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">FBO47JZEFRIBVDM7UA2EPVPMCY</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 12:08:47 GMT</pubDate><author>Jay Ereno, Lisa Marie David</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>中国商务部称欧盟电动汽车初裁违反世贸组织规则</title><description>中国商务部周五表示，欧盟对进口电动汽车（EV）的初步裁决缺乏事实和法律依据，严重违反世界贸易组织（WTO）规则。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-ev-preliminary-ruling-violate-wto-rules-china-ministry-says-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">UNZQ2QVR6ZJQPNS3Q6BFXCHLH4</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:40:35 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Business</category><category>Autos &amp; Transportation</category></item><item><title>斐济总理将于8月12日至21日访华</title><description>中国外交部周五表示，斐济总理西蒂维尼·拉布卡将于周一至8月21日访问中国，欢迎两国有机会建立战略关系。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">Z3YEXDCAGRN7PGO7A42S2UJYCE</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 08:02:47 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>World</category><category>Asia Pacific</category></item><item><title>中国7月份银行贷款将下降，北京将重点关注政策支持</title><description>周五路透调查显示，尽管央行加大了对经济的政策支持力度，但受信贷需求不温不火和季节性因素拖累，中国7月份新增人民币贷款可能较上月大幅下降。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">JQVP67KKARKJRBF4UK2XJMNQUM</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:17:52 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Markets</category><category>Asian Markets</category></item><item><title>随着国内航空公司向海外扩张，外国航空公司对中国失去了兴趣</title><description>由于俄罗斯广阔空域飞往欧洲和北美的北方航线较短，中国航空公司享有成本优势。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">XG2PVHKM2BMJPEAM6GAMOWEEJU</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:56:30 GMT</pubDate><author>Lisa Barrington</author><category>Business</category><category>Aerospace &amp; Defense</category></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求一些券商对债券交易进行合规检查</title><description>三名知情人士表示，中国证券监管机构已下令一些券商检查其债券交易活动，当局试图遏制对中国政府债券的疯狂购买。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">H5WMHRT5PRK6TFJ2LP2IW5OKAA</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:57:39 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Sustainability</category><category>Boards, Policy &amp; Regulation</category></item><item><title>天气因素导致中国消费价格上涨；国内需求依然疲软</title><description>中国脆弱的消费领域一直是北京关注的主要焦点，因为疲软的内需拖累了世界第二大经济体，同时制造业活动萎缩。</description><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">NLNVKPYOIRPNJJEBHOMXE4OOSY</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate><author>Reuters</author><category>Markets</category><category>Asian Markets</category></item></channel></rss>